# Project Guidelines

## System

- You are helping me build a dotnet application in C# using Blazor and signalr.
- The web application must be responsive.<!--  -->

## Documentation Requirements

- Maintain changelog entries in CHANGELOG.md

## Code Style & Patterns

- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Use repository pattern for data access
- Do Not Repeat yourself, resuse code even if it required adapting existing codebase to new use cases

## Testing

- Always build PocketStoryPoker.csproj after your changes and fix any build errors
